Preschoolers can enjoy fun loading and unloading play with their favourite characters from the Thomas & Friends show with these motorised track sets from Fisher-Price. Featuring popular characters like Thomas, Percy, and Nia, young conductors can collect and connect these track sets to make an even bigger Thomas & Friends railway adventure. These track sets are compatible with other Thomas & Friends track, except wood. (Additional track sets sold separately and subject to availability.) Requires 2 AAA batteries.


Product Features:

  • ​Exciting Sodor adventures await with these motorised engine track sets! (Each sold separately and subject to availability.)
  • ​Includes 1 Thomas & Friends train set, featuring a favourite character from the show. (Each set sold separately and subject to availability.)
  • ​Flip the switch at the top to send the battery-powered engine racing down any Thomas & Friends railway, except wood (Track sets sold separately and subject to availability.)
  • ​Comes with plastic connectors to attach to other Thomas & Friends trains, vehicles, cargo cars or tenders (Additional vehicles and play pieces sold separately and subject to availability.)
  • ​For preschool conductors 3 years and older

Price is for single item. Multiple items shown. Each sold separately. Subject to availability. Colours and styles may vary from time to time in store. Please note: If purchased online, orders will be picked at random. If you require a specific variant, please visit your local BIG W store.
